  "message": "\ud83d\udcdd docs: add console v0.3.20 to version dropdown (#1480)\n\nLatest stable release kubestellar/console@v0.3.20 shipped 2026-04-12.\nAdds the entry to CONSOLE_VERSIONS in src/config/versions.ts and the\nmatching row in public/config/shared.json.\n\nNot set as latest \u2014 console dropdown defaults to main.\n\nThe version branch (docs/console/0.3.20) will be created from the\npost-merge main after this PR lands, so the new version actually\nappears in its own dropdown.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
